    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the Q train down to the ocean and explore a brand new location in <strong>Plant Therapy: Coney Island Plus! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078370/extras/c00e626203171e88125358aaf8129a29.poster.avif?t=1731617910\" width=596 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078370/extras/c00e626203171e88125358aaf8129a29.webm?t=1731617910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078370/extras/c00e626203171e88125358aaf8129a29.mp4?t=1731617910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have fun decorating two new BIG apartments with new plants, furniture and artwork. These apartments feature stunning views and cozy outdoor areas.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078370/extras/2ddb304afe173ab50339b6b5068ce9d9.poster.avif?t=1731617910\" width=596 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078370/extras/2ddb304afe173ab50339b6b5068ce9d9.webm?t=1731617910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078370/extras/2ddb304afe173ab50339b6b5068ce9d9.mp4?t=1731617910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And that's not all! <strong>Coney Island Plus</strong> allows you to paint and wallpaper the walls of ALL of your apartments in Plant Therapy. Head over to the new shop, Rainbow &amp; Co. to apply that extra bit of splash you are missing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 new apartments in Coney Island. Your apartments have views of the ocean and the amusement park! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A brand new shop: Rainbow &amp; Co. featuring:<br>        -100+ wallpapers, murals, and decals to decorate any of the apartments <br>        -225+ paint colors to change the wall color or baseboard colors in each apartment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14+ new plants</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ new art and furniture options including a new storage unit in a variety of colors.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
